SharpNES v0.3 (2/27/05)

* Gtk# support added, now with menus!
* Emulation play/pause support (space bar)
* For platforms that support it, fullscreen ('f' key while playing)

SharpNES v0.2 (1/3/05)

* SaveRAM added
* A handful of new mappers were added
* Game specific fixes were included (for Zelda, Battle of Olympus, Legacy of the Wizard and others)
* Sprite 0 hit fixes
* Added optional debug mode (recompile with the FOURSCREEN option)
* CPU optimized (50-75% faster)
* Speed throttling added
* Mappers standardized for a little better compatibility


SharpNES v0.1 (12/17/04)

* Initial Release
